snippet.textDisplay: Mashallah, Mashallah, Mashallah - The experience of watching Farida Khanum Ji has left me speechless and paralyzed. Her God given abilities are unparalleled.  I have heard many sing this Ghazal, but have never understood it the way I have today after hearing this presentation and at this time in her life.  What a precedence she has set!!!  I pray that Allah grant her a long life that is full of  happiness as she has provided so many of us with over the years.
